#: ../../library/base64.rst:131 ../../library/base64.rst:179
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Optional *casefold* is a flag specifying whether a lowercase alphabet is "
"acceptable as input.  For security purposes, the default is ``False``."
msgstr ""
